</P>
<P>
   _ ``Hercules''
</P>
<P>
   ``All other women are like the second pressing of the grape.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Temujin (John Wayne) in ``The Conqueror'' (MCMLVI)
</P>
<P>
   ``My breasts are full of love and life. My hips are round and
