<P>
   Messalina: ``Is there nothing human in your religion?''
</P>
<P>
   Demetrius: ``Well, there's no commandment that says a woman
can't talk like a fool.''
</P>
<P>
   Messalina: ``Be careful, Demetrius. My claws can be sharper than
